	<content><![CDATA[const averageBy = (arr, fn) =>
  arr.map(typeof fn === 'function' ? fn : val => val[fn]).reduce((acc, val) => acc + val, 0) /
  arr.length;]]></content>
	<description>Returns the average of an array, after mapping each element to a value using the provided function.  Use `Array.map()` to map each element to the value returned by `fn`, `Array.reduce()` to add each value to an accumulator, initialized with a value of `0`, divide by the `length` of the array.</description>
